POST api/v1/role/create

** jwt token required **

    request:{
    "name: ...
    "description": ...
    }

    response:{
                'success': True,
                'message': 'Role created successfully',
                'role': {
                    'id': role.id,
                    'name': role.name,
                    'description': role.description,
                }
    }
