POST api/v1/permission/create

** jwt token required **

    request:{
    "name: ...
    "description": ...
    "code": ....
    }

    response:{
                'success': True,
                'message': 'permission created successfully',
                'permission': {
                    'code': permission.code,
                    'name': permission.name,
                    'description': permission.description,
                }
    }
