POST api/v1/rolePermission/create

** jwt token required **

    request:{
    "permission": ...
    "role": ...
    }
    ** you should send permission and role id to get response **

     response:{
                'success': True,
                'message': 'rolePermission created successfully',
                'rolePermission': {
                    'permissionName': rolePermission.permission.name,
                    'roleName': rolePermission.role.name,
                }
            }
