PUT/PATCH api/v1/users/password/change

** jwt token required **

request:{
    "confirm_password":....
    "new_password": ....
    "current_password": ...
}

** only confirm and new password are mandatory **

response:{
            "success": True,
            "message": "Password updated successfully",
            "data": {
                "user_id": request.user.id,
                "username": request.user.username
            }
}
